title: Aquire More Skills
itunes:title: Aquire More Skills
description:
Episode 275 - "Don't wish for it to be easier, wish for more skills" In order to become the person that you want to become you must acquire more skills and more knowledge. Whether you are an entrepreneur or and employee the only way to make more money is to make yourself more valuable to them marketplace and the way to do that is to gain more knowledge.
